1.title: Travel Log I: Austin, TX
1.plot: Open Road Tattoo Tour kicks off in Austin Texas during SXSW 2018. Justin Weatherholtz, Paul Dobleman and Brian Thurow do their first guest spot at Rock of Ages Tattoo. The cast witness the largest bat colony in North America.

2.title: Travel Log II: Dallas, TX
2.plot: The artists make their way to Dallas where they are met with the hospitality of Elm Street Tattoo and owner Oliver Peck. The crew play mini golf inside Oliver's home aka "Pecker's Playhouse."

3.title: Travel Log III: Denver, CO
3.plot: The artists make a stop in Santa Fe, New Mexico where they visit Meow Wolf and meet artist Mikey Rae. Austin Maples joins the tour in Denver as the group guest at Brian Thurow's shop Dedication Tattoo.

imdb.plot outline: Part road trip, part body art show, part life changing experience. 4 tattoo artists travel across the country and become featured artists at 11 of the country's top influential tattoo shops. The artists seek new inspiration within the versatile and expansive discipline of tattooing through their experiences on the road as they engage with fellow tattoo artists and tattoo lovers on the ground.
